      <title>国际货币基金组织首席称特朗普的关税议程为“重大风险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-tariff-agenda-called-a-significant-risk-by-imf-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织董事总经理克里斯塔利娜·乔治耶夫（Kristalina Georgieva）警告说，唐纳德·特朗普总统的全面关税运动“在成长缓慢的时候对全球前景构成了重大风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-tariff-agenda-called-a-significant-risk-by-imf-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税在推出之前的最后几个小时内得到了磨练</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/how-trump-s-tariffs-were-honed-in-final-hours-before-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易萨尔沃已经完成了多年。细节归结为最后时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/how-trump-s-tariffs-were-honed-in-final-hours-before-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:28:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州施加全天禁止学校的手机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据旨在改善儿童心理健康的新预算协议，纽约州立法领导人已同意禁止在公立学校使用智能手机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国希望促进俱乐部，伦敦汗的新权力的酒吧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/uk-looks-to-boost-clubs-pubs-with-new-powers-for-london-s-khan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正在寻找为酒吧，俱乐部和餐馆削减繁文tape节的方法，以促进英国的夜间经济，包括通过向伦敦市长萨迪克·汗（Sadiq Khan）提供新的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/uk-looks-to-boost-clubs-pubs-with-new-powers-for-london-s-khan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州说，特朗普以5.1亿美元的资金冻结了布朗。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-to-hit-brown-with-510-million-funding-freeze-nyt-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《纽约时报》报道，特朗普政府有望在学校对校园的反犹太主义的反应中封锁5.1亿美元的联邦赠款和合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-to-hit-brown-with-510-million-funding-freeze-nyt-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:56:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍克尔说，特朗普的关税已经在伤害纽约经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hochul-says-trump-s-tariffs-are-already-hurting-new-york-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长凯西·霍赫尔（Kathy Hochul）说，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的广泛关税推动已经达到纽约的经济状况，加拿大旅游业和跨境购物降低了营业税收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hochul-says-trump-s-tariffs-are-already-hurting-new-york-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:38:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德勤在削减支出的情况下解雇政府顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/deloitte-to-lay-off-government-consultants-amid-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉高管和工人之间的电话的人说，德勤有限责任公司计划在其政府咨询团队中裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/deloitte-to-lay-off-government-consultants-amid-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 21:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官权衡鄙视特朗普官员对被驱逐出境的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/judge-mulls-contempt-order-for-trump-officials-over-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官说，特朗普政府官员违反了他的命令，即立即停止被怀疑是帮派成员的委内瑞拉人的命令，并补充说，他可能会引起他们的蔑视。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/judge-mulls-contempt-order-for-trump-officials-over-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 20:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普给中国XI一个赢得关税打击世界的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提高对所有国家 /地区的关税的举动将特别严重打击中国的经济。但这也是在XI赋予罕见的开放，以加深整体关系，包括与美国在亚洲及其他地区的关键盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫在附件中调整了14个关税水平。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/white-house-annex-shows-slight-tariff-level-changes-for-some</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为美国互惠的关税设定为十多个国家，唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税推出的第一天不仅为经济后果做好了准备，而且对他们可能面临的比率感到困惑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/white-house-annex-shows-slight-tariff-level-changes-for-some</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
